{"tid":1242333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醒啦！港豬！","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:00:58.000Z","uid":151558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb212423055d5080657f6a7d6777929bf4cdb54","tid":1242333,"uid":151558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:23:27.000Z","msg":"淋病推唔到送中就陰d陰d推咩高鐵同大嶼<br />\n好明顯係中共想洗撚晒香港🇭🇰d錢<br />\n等你地班港豬生活又窮又辛苦<br />\n然後用陰招等你屈服、冇得反抗！<br />\n<br />\n唔好掉以輕心以為乜事都冇，<br />\n香港最難熬嘅時候依家先啱啱開始。<br />\n<br />\n為左你地嘅家唔好畀人蠶食晒<br />\n唔該你地企硬唔好輕易屈服！<br />\n<br />\nNow or never"},{"pid":"06d838437c1880c4910f39f33f7b96ec031882ce","tid":1242333,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543550805aa4fb8580483db4b64ba526e7b97003","tid":1242333,"uid":95193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"成段野都同意 唯一唔同意就係咪都咁窮咁辛苦"},{"pid":"a8b7ca5415370a314265fdd3ef6e49cb24a3027b","tid":1242333,"uid":151558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"543550805aa4fb8580483db4b64ba526e7b97003","tid":1242333,"uid":95193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"成段野都同意 唯一唔同意就係咪都咁窮咁辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"依家窮但生活都算過得去<br />\n中共係要令你生活過唔去<br />\n滿滿屈服"},{"pid":"819a9a28b241009fe75037281642df6b0b58bcbc","tid":1242333,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:58:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港豬：「致敬？搞到我地無工開無飯食！」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDvKuTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDvKuTj.png&h=cfb5244e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XC7g5rF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXC7g5rF.png&h=9a15a17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁鍾意返工去大灣區返啦dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FQRUmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt